context.text: List of United States Air Force air mobility squadrons - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
List of United States Air Force air mobility squadrons

This is a list of United States Air Force air mobility squadrons . It covers units considered to be part of the Mobility Air Force (MAF) such as aeromedical evacuation, air refueling, and airlift squadrons and serves as a break out of the comprehensive List of United States Air Force squadrons . Units in this list are assigned to nearly every Major Command in the United States Air Force .
